      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "\n",
        "**1. Problem Statement**\n",
        "Predict credit default to minimize financial loss.\n",
        "\n",
        "**2. Dataset**\n",
        "UCI Credit Card Default Dataset (~30k records).\n",
        "\n",
        "**3. Challenges**\n",
        "\n",
        "Imbalanced data\n",
        "\n",
        "Cost-sensitive errors\n",
        "\n",
        "**4. Approach**\n",
        "\n",
        "EDA\n",
        "\n",
        "Feature engineering\n",
        "\n",
        "Class-weighted models\n",
        "\n",
        "Threshold tuning\n",
        "\n",
        "**5. Evaluation Metrics**\n",
        "\n",
        "Recall\n",
        "\n",
        "PR-AUC\n",
        "\n",
        "ROC-AUC\n",
        "\n",
        "**6. Results**\n",
        "\n",
        "Recall improved from X → Y\n",
        "\n",
        "Estimated loss reduced by ₹X\n",
        "\n",
        "**7. Tools**\n",
        "Python, Pandas, Scikit-learn, XGBoost, SHAP\n",
        "\n",
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "B2A4XThj23n5"
      }
    },

