            "Estimated Loss (₹): 30700000\n"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "📌 Interview killer line:\n",
        "\n",
        "“I optimized recall to reduce financial loss rather than chasing accuracy.”"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "3xJZJjJDi4ez"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "🧠 What You MUST Be Able to Explain\n",
        "\n",
        "Why PR-AUC > ROC-AUC\n",
        "\n",
        "Why threshold tuning matters\n",
        "\n",
        "How business cost shapes ML decisions\n",
        "\n",
        "Tradeoff between precision & recall"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "1RzSsVlki-3m"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "**🔥 STEP 6: Explainability, Feature Importance & Project Packaging**"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "5URZZeUjjDWU"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "🎯 Objective\n",
        "\n",
        "Explain why the model predicts default\n",
        "\n",
        "Identify key drivers of risk\n",
